<section sectnbr = "5E">
<servcat sctnbr = "05" scnbr = "05">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENCP70A5506024" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Key Interlock Cable Inspection (Ignition Switch Model)
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Shift select lever to P range and set ignition switch to ACC.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
While pushing shift lock manual release button (1), press the select lever button (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IBP50A550025.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.355mm" ver = "01" gw = "221" gh = "132"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
At the condition in step 2), check that ignition switch cannot be turned from ACC to LOCK position.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A510071.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "24.326mm" ver = "01" gw = "72" gh = "52"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Then release the select lever button. Check that ignition switch can be turned from ACC to LOCK position.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If faulty condition is found, adjust key interlock cable. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5506023"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A510072.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "24.326mm" ver = "01" gw = "73" gh = "52"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
